{"tid":1507251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一段歷史說明 點解荃灣擋子彈大叔必須推上國際","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T19:38:58.000Z","uid":86221,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ed00355b216a4461acedfcef472e9469ef00361e","tid":1507251,"uid":86221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/26/132856_ef82ac887370fa976383cd582699bde8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F26%2F132856_ef82ac887370fa976383cd582699bde8.jpg&h=9f39ec21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2018/01/30/world/00xp-Photo_xp/00xp-Photo_xp-master1050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2Fworld%2F00xp-Photo_xp%2F00xp-Photo_xp-master1050.jpg&h=fcbe4d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五十年前的今天（2月1日），南越國家警察總監平靜地走向站在西貢一條街道上的一名俘虜，對準他的頭部開了一槍。<br />\n<br />\n幾英尺開外，美聯社攝影記者艾迪&middot;亞當斯(Eddie Adams)緊盯著相機取景器，用一小塊黑白膠片捕捉到了槍擊發生的瞬間。<br />\n<br />\n警察總監阮玉鸞(Nguyen Ngoc Loan)將軍背對相機，右臂伸直，左臂垂在身側。俘虜阮文斂(Nguyen Van Lem)是越共戰士，但沒有穿制服，只穿著格子襯衫和黑色短褲。他的雙手被反銬著。儘管有30多歲，看上去比一個男孩大不了多少。子彈的衝擊力令他面部扭曲。<br />\n<br />\n到了翌日早上，全美各地報紙的頭版令他生命的最後一刻被永遠銘記，其中也包括《紐約時報》。這張照片與NBC的錄像一起，讓美國人對越南戰爭的殘酷性有了清晰的認識，並推動了公共輿論的決定性轉變。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20180202/vietnam-execution-photo/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fasia-pacific%2F20180202%2Fvietnam-execution-photo%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=d2e539db\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20180202/vietnam-execution-photo/zh-hant/</a>"},{"pid":"83dd692af1f70fed6dd2153d740b27da1f26252d","tid":1507251,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:31:08.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=27881fe5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"6196be06582c7b5af61807010cf2652f4ffe7a9b","tid":1507251,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"615a9a0d4dcd7ba75af50812801c299a75e286a1","tid":1507251,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:32:24.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益  對付白色恐怖嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506382\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506382</a>"},{"pid":"e82750fcc053a4cd05a0869bdcf4f71ff7101200","tid":1507251,"uid":119596,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我去過越南個博物館都有呢張相..真係好震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戰爭嘅殘酷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有邊個唔想和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係有啲野我地就算豁出去,不惜代價,甚至條命都要去爭取<img src=\"/assets/face